title: Mortal Kombat Original Soundtrack (Nintendo, not movie)
description:
This is the first mortal kombat soundtrack that ever came out. It IS NOT the one for the mortal kombat movie. This album game out to promote the mortal kombat super nintendo game.

Genre: Techno
Year: 1994
Artist: The Immortals



1. Johnny Cage (Prepare Yourself)
2. Kano (Use Your Might
3. Sub-Zero (Chinese Ninja Warrior)
4. Liu Kang (Born in China)
5. Techno Syndrome (Mortal Kombat)
6. Scorpion (Lost Soul Bent on Revenge)
7. Sonya (Go Go Go)
8. Rayden (Eternal Life)
9. Goro (The Outerworld Prince)
10. Hypnotic House [Mortal Kombat] 

It use to be huge at rave and drugs parties when it first came out. Solid techno and dance beats.
